PrecisConfirmation of the request made to the Hon. Rev. Walter Franklin McLean, Member of Parliament for the constituency of Waterloo, to accompany the Secretary of State and his official delegation on their visit to Lusaka, Zambia, and Windhoek, Namibia, in order to meet with Mr. Nelson Mandela and other Commonwealth and African leaders (Feb. 23 to March 5, 1990).
